item.title: Server source preferably no client
item.dc:creator: @Spades Spades
item.description:
@Spades wrote:

A good starting source is Delta or Allstar Scape

Allstar is what I started on, but I found that it had many glitches in it, but it is good because that teaches you how to fix glitches.

After awhile I fixed most of the glitches and I moved onto Delta, that is what I am working on right now, I will most likely continue to work with this source seeing how good it is.
